 know, a little more than average and so I was disappointed. The food is cooked well and fresh but not amazing or adventurous to the tastebuds. BUT. The dessert. We shared the "spicy ume (plum) sake sorbet & jelly". Now THAT'S creative and adventurous. It's spicy but so sweet and refreshing. I can't even describe the taste and experience of it--it's like nothing else. Definitely try it!
